#

Avocado Tomato Toast with Feta

10 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh FiberLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A fresh and vibrant toast topped with creamy avocado, juicy tomatoes, and a sprinkle of feta cheese.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • tomato: 1 medium
  • feta cheese: 1/4 cup, crumbled
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • basil leaves: a few, for garnish
